// Viewer Store
// Zustand store tracking which artifact (document or diagram) is currently displayed in the viewer pane.

State shape:
  currentView: { type: 'document' | 'diagram', id: string } | null

FUNCTION navigateToArtifact(id, type)                                   EXPORT
  Set currentView to { type, id }.

---

FUNCTION reset()                                                        EXPORT
  Set currentView to null.
